@RagAppBasic_HostAddress = https://localhost:7249

### HealthController - Check API keys
GET {{RagAppBasic_HostAddress}}/health/keys
Accept: application/json

### QueryController - Ask a question
POST {{RagAppBasic_HostAddress}}/query
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
{
    "question": "When will I receive my refund?",
    "topK": 3
}

### IngestController - Upload files for ingestion
POST {{RagAppBasic_HostAddress}}/ingest/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Example for file upload (use your HTTP client to attach .pdf/.txt/.md files)
# files: [yourfile.pdf, yourfile.txt]
